ata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/viral-spread-tweet-750x496.png" data-large-file="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/viral-spread-tweet-1090x721.png" /></a></p> Twitter 有一个社区注释功能，尝试标记包含以下内容的帖子：<p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/bloomberg/" rel="tag">彭博社</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/misinformation/" rel="tag">错误信息</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/twitter/" rel="tag">推特</a></p>]]>; </description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p> <a href="https://flowingdata.com/2023/11/29/failed-community-notes-to-stop-misinformation-on-twitter/"><img width="750" height="496" src="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/viral-spread-tweet-750x496.png" class="attachment-medium size-medium wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/viral-spread-tweet-750x496.png 750w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/viral-spread-tweet-1090x721.png 1090w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/viral-spread-tweet-210x139.png 210w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/viral-spread-tweet-768x508.png 768w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/viral-spread-tweet-1536x1016.png 1536w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/viral-spread-tweet.png 1732w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-attachment-id="72749" data-permalink="https://flowingdata.com/2023/11/29/failed-community-notes-to-stop-misinformation-on-twitter/viral-spread-tweet/" data-orig-file="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/viral-spread-tweet.png" data-orig-size="1732,1146" data-comments-opened="0" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="viral spread tweet" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/viral-spread-tweet-750x496.png" data-large-file="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/viral-spread-tweet-1090x721.png" /></a></p><p> Twitter 有一个社区注释功能，试图标记包含错误信息的帖子。从理论上讲，这可能很有效，而且注释通常内容丰富，但效果很慢，而且通常不足以阻止病毒式推文中错误信息的传播。 <a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2023-israel-hamas-war-misinformation-twitter-community-notes/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzb3VyY2UiOiJTdWJzY3JpYmVyR2lmdGVkQXJ0aWNsZSIsImlhdCI6MTcwMDk3OTg2NCwiZXhwIjoxNzAxNTg0NjY0LCJhcnRpY2xlSWQiOiJTNEdNMDRUMEcxS1cwMSIsImJjb25uZWN0SWQiOiIzRDhGMEEzMTc2MDc0NUM5OTg4NkFCNzA1NDk2RUNEQSJ9.ZJpbXkV6l-WwcPLeJilXWaP-RpRMNISpWGE1AYq75ns">彭博社通过一条推文展示了传播情况</a>。</p><p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/bloomberg/" rel="tag">彭博社</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/misinformation/" rel="tag">错误信息</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/twitter/" rel="tag">推特</a></p>]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 72748 </post-id></item></channel></rss><!-- *´¨)
